FT  27 APR 94 / UK Company News: Rentokil
Rentokil Group is making a further investment of Dollars 1.5m (Pounds
900,000) cash for two US acquisitions.
The companies are Sidwa &amp; Associates, a Dallas interior landscaping concern,
and Comex Commercial Exterminators, a Georgia-based pest control group.
At the same time, Rentokil confirmed the purchase of M and B
Projektbeplanting in the Netherlands for Fl 500,000 (Pounds 200,000) cash.
